# Static utility commands вАФ en-US catalog (batch: help/invite/support/suggest/
# imsafe/permissions). Keys are prefixed with the command name to stay
# globally unique. Note: Fluent continuation lines must not start with
# "*", "[" or "." вАФ hence the leading bullets/emoji before markdown.

help-title = How to trophies 101
help-description =
    Create custom trophies, award them to members and climb the leaderboard!

    рЯПЖ **Trophy management** (requires Manage Server)
    вАҐ `/create` вАФ create a new trophy
    вАҐ `/edit` вАФ edit an existing trophy
    вАҐ `/delete` вАФ delete a trophy
    вАҐ `/award` вАФ award a trophy to a member (inactive trophies can't be given out)
    вАҐ `/revoke` вАФ take an awarded trophy back
    вАҐ `/clear` вАФ reset a member's trophies and score
    вАҐ `/details` вАФ view a trophy's private details

    рЯС• **For everyone**
    вАҐ `/show` вАФ showcase a trophy
    вАҐ `/trophies user | guild` вАФ list a member's or the server's trophies
    вАҐ `/leaderboard` вАФ ranking of members by score

    вЪЩпЄП **Server setup** (requires Manage Server)
    вАҐ `/settings` вАФ configure the bot for this server
    вАҐ `/rewards` вАФ automatic role rewards based on score
    вАҐ `/panel` вАФ auto-updating leaderboard panel
    вАҐ `/panel medals` вАФ auto-updating catalog panel for one category of active trophies
    вАҐ `/panel overview` вАФ auto-updating catalog panel for every category at once
    вАҐ `/link` вАФ mirror another server's panels here, or let another server mirror yours
    вАҐ `/export` вАФ export your server's data

    Who can use each command is controlled by Discord itself: open **Server Settings вЖТ Integrations вЖТ Trophy Bot** to allow or deny commands per role, member or channel.

